            <thetext>The problem is that the space allocated for the Column Menu button is too small. Its container, a qx.ui.table.pane.Clipper object, has its &#39;top&#39; property set to too low a value to allow the rows below it to align with the tree (table) data.

This bug is likely a regression due to some recent changes to Table. git-bisect is likely the right tool to use here.

I won&#39;t have the bandwidth to look into this further for a while. I&#39;d suggest it get reassigned to someone else for faster turn-around. (I do not currently believe the problem is in TreeVirtual; I think it&#39;s in Table.)</thetext>
